project_descr: Support provided and the capacity of the Principal Recipient built to implement the key activities within the grant from Global Fund to fight AIDS, Tuberculosis and Malaria.

outputs.output_descr: The project aims to prevent the spread of HIV/AIDS among the general population by reducing its impacts on the most vulnerable groups of the populations, including injecting drug users, prisoners, sex workers, and men who have sex with men and youth.
donor_name: GLOBAL FUND TO FIGHT AIDS, TUBERCULOSIS

project_title: support to prevent spread of hiv/aids
